这是一份'''中国的著名清真寺列表'''。[[清真寺|清真寺]]是[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]信徒的朝觐之所。中国的第一家清真寺是[[怀圣寺|广州怀圣寺]]，建于627年的[[唐朝|唐朝]]。2014年中国各地有39,135家清真寺，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dzb.rmzxb.com/detail.aspx?id=352820 |title=Strengthen and promote the standardization of mosque management |publisher=[[Chinese_People's_Political_Consultative_Conference|CPPCC]] News |date=2014-12-18 |access-date=2015-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222163343/http://dzb.rmzxb.com/detail.aspx?id=352820 |archive-date=2015-02-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=2015最新中国清真寺数量及分布|url=http://www.chinaislam.net.cn/cms/news/media/201503/03-8001.html|access-date=2021-01-11|website=www.chinaislam.net.cn|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302223922/http://www.chinaislam.net.cn/cms/news/media/201503/03-8001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中2009年有25,000家在中国西北的[[新疆维吾尔自治区|新疆维吾尔自治区]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zqb.cyol.com/content/2009-07/17/content_2761116.htm|title=The amount of mosques in Xinjiang is increasing to near 25,000|publisher=Chinese Youth Daily|date=2009-07-17|access-date=2015-02-22|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022094717/http://zqb.cyol.com/content/2009-07/17/content_2761116.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新疆当地清真寺数量近十年极具攀升，密度高达每530人一座清真寺，为土耳其的两倍之多<ref>[https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20200925-%E6%BE%B3%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%93-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4-%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%B8%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%BA1-6%E4%B8%87%E5%BA%A7-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E6%B1%A1%E8%94%91 澳智库：中国近年拆除、破坏新疆清真寺1.6万座 北京：污蔑] {{Wayback|url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20200925-%E6%BE%B3%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%93-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4-%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%B8%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%BA1-6%E4%B8%87%E5%BA%A7-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E6%B1%A1%E8%94%91 |date=20201107021926 }} 法广，2020年9月25日</ref>，绝对数量位居世界第二<ref>[http://www.humanrights.cn/html/llyj/1/5/2016/0614/18288.html 新疆各族穆斯林享有充分的宗教信仰自由] 中国人权网 2016-06-14</ref>。另說中国共约有20,000 - 45,000家清真寺。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.islam.org.hk/eng/eIslamInChina24.asp |title=Muslims 2014 <!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-08-18 |archive-date=2015-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713052417/http://www.islam.org.hk/eng/eIslamInChina24.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://chinamuslim.per.sg/madrasah/madrasah.htm |title=Madrasahs<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-08-18 |archive-date=2001-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010826074803/http://www.chinamuslim.per.sg/madrasah/madrasah.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://memri.org/bin/articles.cgi?Page=archives&Area=sd&ID=SP72904 |title=MEMRI: Special Dispatch Series - No. 729<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-08-18 |archive-date=2009-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815082633/http://memri.org/bin/articles.cgi?Page=archives&Area=sd&ID=SP72904 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

在中国，[[犹太会堂|犹太会堂]]也被[[中国犹太人|中国犹太人]]称作清真寺。清真寺又叫'''回回堂'''、'''回回寺'''、'''礼拜寺'''、'''真教寺'''、'''清净寺'''。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XULERYYEJo0C&q=huihui+tang+mosque&pg=PA29|title=Islam in China|author=Shoujiang Mi, Jia You|year=2004|publisher=五洲传播出版社|page=29|isbn=7-5085-0533-6|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-date=2021-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211005222426/https://books.google.com/books?id=XULERYYEJo0C&q=huihui+tang+mosque&pg=PA29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6wEMAAAAYAAJ&q=mohammedan+temple+arabic|title=The Chinese repository, Volume 13|year=1844|publisher=Printed for the proprietors|page=31|access-date=2011-05-08|archive-date=2016-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428205026/https://books.google.com/books?id=6wEMAAAAYAAJ&q=mohammedan#q=mohammedan%20temple%20arabic|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[清朝|清朝]]年间，回族清真寺入口都刻有“皇帝万岁，万岁，万万岁”的古碑。<ref>[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_ObcNAAAAIAAJ/page/n269 <!-- pg=290 --> Broomhall 1910], p. 290.</ref>来中国旅游的西方人在[[云南|云南]]、[[宁波|宁波]]的清真寺注意到这些古碑。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xX8jAAAAMAAJ&q=happening+to+see+in+the+mosque,+threshold+as+you+enter+a+tablet+temple+inscription+the+emperor+may+he+live+for+ever+the+emperor+the+everliving#q=happening%20to%20see%20in%20the%20mosque%20threshold%20as%20you%20enter%20a%20tablet%20temple%20inscription%20the%20emperor%20may%20he%20live%20for%20ever%20the%20emperor%20the%20everliving|title=The Chinese repository, Volumes 11-15|year=1842|publisher=Printed for the proprietors.|page=33|access-date=2010-06-28|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820023835/https://books.google.com/books?id=xX8jAAAAMAAJ&pg=RA2-PA33&dq=happening+to+see+in+the+mosque,+threshold+as+you+enter+a+tablet+temple+inscription+the+emperor+may+he+live+for+ever+the+emperor+the+everliving#q=happening%20to%20see%20in%20the%20mosque%20threshold%20as%20you%20enter%20a%20tablet%20temple%20inscription%20the%20emperor%20may%20he%20live%20for%20ever%20the%20emperor%20the%20everliving|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hUEswLE4SWUC&q=mosques+tablets+wishing+the+emperor+long+life+prominent+position+entrance+mosque|title=China's Muslim Hui community: migration, settlement and sects|author=Michael Dillon|year=1999|publisher=Curzon Press|location=Richmond|page=77|isbn=0-7007-1026-4|access-date=2010-06-28|archive-date=2016-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427171756/https://books.google.com/books?id=hUEswLE4SWUC&dq=ma+anliang&q=wooden+tablet#q=mosques%20tablets%20wishing%20the%20emperor%20long%20life%20prominent%20position%20entrance%20mosque|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Hagras|first=Hamada|title=An Ancient Mosque in Ningbo, China "Historical and Architectural Study"|date=2017|url=http://103.17.76.13/index.php/JIA/article/view/3851/pdf|journal=Journal of Islamic Architecture|volume=4|issue=3|pages=102–113|doi=10.18860/jia.v4i3.3851|doi-access=free|access-date=2020-01-08|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617185521/http://103.17.76.13/index.php/JIA/article/view/3851/pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大多数清真寺都有特定的共同点，但和其他宗教一样，中国伊斯兰教建筑也通过自身风格反映当地建筑。中国以美丽的类似庙宇的清真寺闻名。但在中国西部，清真寺像[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[中亚|中亚]]的清真寺那样有高而细的光塔、弯曲的拱门和圆形屋顶，以及独特的多层入口。在中国西北中国[[回族|回族]]建造清真寺的地方都混合了东西方风格，将有墙的庭院内的佛教风格的屋顶通过有小型圆屋顶和光塔的拱道外倾。<ref>Saudi Aramco World, July/August 1985 , page 3035</ref>

回族清真寺的建筑风格因[[伊斯蘭教派|教派]]而异。传统主义者[[格迪目|格迪目]][[哈乃斐派|哈乃斐派]]逊尼派受中国文化影响，建立看似中国庙宇的清真寺。改革派现代主义者（但原本启发自[[瓦哈比派|瓦哈比派]]）[[依赫瓦尼派|依赫瓦尼派]]将他们的清真寺建造成看起来像阿拉伯风格的清真寺。随着改革派在中国的影响越来越大，一些中国伊斯兰风格的清真寺被重建为阿拉伯风格，例如[[韦州清真大寺|韦州清真大寺]]。这引起了中国政府的不满，并最终导致了中国清真寺建筑重新中国化的反击。

